[Vaccine hesitancy is a global problem that appears to be growing. One would think education of parents would solve the problem, but that doesn't appear to be the case as people reject the scientific evidence demonstrating the safety and efficacy of the MMR (measles, mumps, rubella) vaccine. Losing a child to a vaccine-preventable disease is totally unnecessary and a terrible thing. - Mod.LK

